#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an7.12"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.12:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.12:0.2"
msgid "2. Anusayavagga "
msgstr "2. Tendencies "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 12. Dutiyaanusayasutta → anusayappahānasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an7.12:0.3"
msgid "12. Dutiyaanusayasutta "
msgstr "12. Underlying Tendencies (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an7.12:1.1"
msgid "“Sattannaṃ, bhikkhave, anusayānaṃ pahānāya samucchedāya brahmacariyaṃ vussati. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, the spiritual life is lived to give up and cut out these seven underlying tendencies. "

msgctxt "an7.12:1.2"
msgid "Katamesaṃ sattannaṃ? "
msgstr "What seven? "

msgctxt "an7.12:1.3"
msgid "Kāmarāgānusayassa pahānāya samucchedāya brahmacariyaṃ vussati, paṭighānusayassa … pe … "
msgstr "The underlying tendencies of sensual desire, repulsion, views, doubt, conceit, desire to be reborn, and ignorance. "

msgctxt "an7.12:1.4"
msgid "diṭṭhānusayassa … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.12:1.5"
msgid "vicikicchānusayassa … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.12:1.6"
msgid "mānānusayassa … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.12:1.7"
msgid "bhavarāgānusayassa … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.12:1.8"
msgid "avijjānusayassa pahānāya samucchedāya brahmacariyaṃ vussati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.12:1.9"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, sattannaṃ anusayānaṃ pahānāya samucchedāya brahmacariyaṃ vussati. "
msgstr "The spiritual life is lived to give up and cut out these seven underlying tendencies. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an7.12:2.1"
msgid "Yato ca kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno kāmarāgānusayo pahīno hoti ucchinnamūlo tālāvatthukato anabhāvaṅkato āyatiṃ anuppādadhammo. "
msgstr "When a mendicant has given up the underlying tendencies of sensual desire, repulsion, views, doubt, conceit, desire to be reborn, and ignorance—cut them off at the root, made them like a palm stump, obliterated them, so they are unable to arise in the future—"

msgctxt "an7.12:2.2"
msgid "Paṭighānusayo … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.12:2.3"
msgid "diṭṭhānusayo … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.12:2.4"
msgid "vicikicchānusayo … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.12:2.5"
msgid "mānānusayo … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.12:2.6"
msgid "bhavarāgānusayo … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.12:2.7"
msgid "avijjānusayo pahīno hoti ucchinnamūlo tālāvatthukato anabhāvaṅkato āyatiṃ anuppādadhammo. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.12:2.8"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, bhikkhu acchecchi taṇhaṃ, vivattayi saṃyojanaṃ, sammā mānābhisamayā antamakāsi dukkhassā”ti. "
msgstr "they’re called a mendicant who has cut off craving, untied the fetters, and by rightly comprehending conceit has made an end of suffering.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.12:2.9"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
